    The template inherits the DOM structure from local/csi_coursebuilder/templates/messages/base template.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * body
    * viewrequestdetails
    * allrequestsurl

    Example context (json):
    {
        "body": "This is the body of the message",
        "viewrequestdetails": "https://avenue.ca/classroom/local_csi_coursebuilder/viewrequestdetails.php?id=1",
        "allrequestsurl": "https://avenue.ca/classroom/local/csi_coursebuilder/eunitsapproval.php?id=1"
    }
}}

